676
01:07:33,898 --> 01:07:39,397
♫ Just because of your love ♫

677
01:07:39,398 --> 01:07:44,298
♫ I won't let you go ♫

678
01:08:02,448 --> 01:08:04,258
起きたか？

679
01:08:23,748 --> 01:08:25,808
じゃあ　帰ろう

680
01:08:43,828 --> 01:08:50,937
♫ It's not longing, it's not regret ♫

681
01:08:50,938 --> 01:08:58,058
♫ What is this? This feeling that
